data.description: Don't miss this charming home with many built ins china cabinet, books shelves, etc.  Enjoy you coffee on front patio or enjoy coffee on back patio both covered.   Two bedrooms with a flex room that could be use for dining/den 3rd bedroom/office. Back yard with private pvc fencing around most of yard,  Owner said there is hardwood flooring under carpet in front room.  Washer and dry convey.
